---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 485
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=Repentance, Renewal and Awakening
By: Johannes Kelpius
---
We must not be deceived. Without inward prayer there is no conquest
over the flesh, and without this conquest over the flesh, no true
inward prayer; and without this the one and the other is no
conversion, no true internal life, no perfection or Christianity.
